- size can modified: can add/remove item

> Create
ArrayList <Type> name = new ArrayList <Type> ();

> Add items
name.add()

> Access item
name.get(indexNo)

> Change
name.set(indexNo, "new")

> Remove
name.remove(indexNo)

> Remove all elements
name.clear()

> Size
name.size()

> Loop
for (int i = 0; i < name.length(); i++){
  System.out.println(name.get(i));
  }

or

for (Type i : name){
  System.out.println(i);
}

> Type
Integer, Boolean, Character, Double

> Sort
Collections.sort(name)

